414
00:18:07,550 --> 00:18:09,350
He's perfect in my eyes.

415
00:18:09,350 --> 00:18:11,990
In my eyes, he's not.

416
00:18:12,430 --> 00:18:14,270
Although he has many strengths,

417
00:18:14,430 --> 00:18:15,950
