418
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:19,150
He can be like a kid sometimes.

419
00:18:19,430 --> 00:18:20,470
Childish.

420
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:21,940
Bad-tempered.

421
00:18:22,380 --> 00:18:23,990
When he hurt people,

422
00:18:23,990 --> 00:18:25,550
