00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:01,660
Stop living in the past.

437
00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:04,790
That's just your imagination.

438
00:19:05,470 --> 00:19:07,670
Don't let a false imagination

439
00:19:07,670 --> 00:19:09,070
